FleetIds.description: Unique identifier for the fleet(s) you want to retrieve utilization data for. To request utilization data for all fleets, leave this parameter empty.

Limit.description: Maximum number of results to return. Use this parameter with NextToken to get results as a set of sequential pages. This parameter is ignored when the request specifies one or a list of fleet IDs.

NextToken.description: Token indicating the start of the next sequential page of results. Use the token that is returned with a previous call to this action. To specify the start of the result set, do not specify a value. This parameter is ignored when the request specifies one or a list of fleet IDs.
